      <title>印度煤炭转向债务市场来资助其电力项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/coal-india-turns-to-debt-markets-to-fund-its-power-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财务总监Mukesh Agrawal表示，州矿工Coal India Ltd.计划为其非开采企业（例如可再生项目和热电厂）筹集债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/coal-india-turns-to-debt-markets-to-fund-its-power-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 06:57:00 GMT</pubDate>
