      <title>特朗普的交易被颠覆了，因为国债返回击败了我们的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/treasuries-are-beating-us-stocks-for-first-time-since-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从唐纳德·特朗普当选总统以来，美国国债现在胜过股票，一些战略家说，这些收益的空间可以运行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/treasuries-are-beating-us-stocks-for-first-time-since-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 02:01:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油降低了特朗普的关税，欧佩克+计划提高产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于特朗普政府对包括中国在内的美国贸易伙伴的关税生效，而欧佩克+标志着恢复停止产量的计划，因此近三个月的最低损失从近三个月来的最低损失延长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 23:29:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票鞭子，关税后石油下降：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国对唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税的回应后，股票弥补了损失，并避免了世界两大经济体之间的全面贸易战争。财政部的产量消除了，而石油下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 22:46:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟对银行交易规则的民意调查，包括调整选项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/eu-poll-on-bank-trading-rules-to-offer-option-of-tweaking-them</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据彭博新闻社（Bloomberg News）的一份文件，欧盟计划的有关银行交易业务的监管变更的民意调查将概述各种选择，包括提供三年的优惠。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/eu-poll-on-bank-trading-rules-to-offer-option-of-tweaking-them</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 17:34:15 GMT</pubDate>
